<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c1">"ص"</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نائب فعل غير معمول ولا ... فضلة اسم الفعل والمجدي افعلا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يأتي كثيرا، وبمعنى <span class="c1">"فعلا"</span> ... و<span class="c1">"أفعل"</span> استعماله تقللا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كـ<span class="c1">"أف"</span> <span class="c1">"هيهات"</span> <span class="c1">"نزال"</span> <span class="c1">"وي"</span> و<span class="c1">"صه"</span> ... <span class="c1">"شتان"</span> <span class="c1">"أوه"</span> تيد<span class="c1">" "</span>هيا<span class="c1">" "</span>هيت<span class="c1">" "</span>مه<span class="c1">"<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>"إيه<span class="c1">" "</span>آمين<span class="c1">" "</span>حيهل<span class="c1">" "</span>وشكانا<span class="c1">" ... "</span>سرعان<span class="c1">" "</span>ويها<span class="c1">" "</span>بله<span class="c1">" "</span>ها<span class="c1">" "</span>بطآنا<span class="c1">"<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>"ويها<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(١)</span> و"</span>واها<span class="c1">" كذاك و"</span>هلم<span class="c1">" ... في قول من تجريدها حتما يؤم<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>واحكم لها بحكم الأفعال التي ... تنوب عنها ذاكرا قصور "تي"<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) س ش ط ع ط "واها وواها".</p> </div>